# .cursor/rules — Cursor overlay
#
# Specializes AGENTS.md for Cursor agents. Never relaxes GROUNDING.md.

## Always
- Read `AGENTS.md` and `GROUNDING.md` before any edit.
- Update `.agent/plan.md` before edits.
- Respect path allowlist in `AGENTS.md`.

## Never
- Write to paths outside the allowlist.
- Run destructive commands without explicit user confirmation.
- Send red-class data to any tool, log, or model.

## Tools
- Prefer `Edit` (patch) over full-file rewrites.
- Use `Search` before `Read` to minimize context use.

## Verification
- Run lint + tests before declaring done.
- Append a `Decisions log` entry for each non-trivial decision.
